HIP Database











UIC Impact is the University of Illinois at Chicago’s commitment that all students will have the opportunity to apply their learning to real world challenges through high impact engagement.












            Customize Your UIC Experience
          Heading link



 
Copy link



            Learn how you can customize your UIC Experience by completing these three phases.
          






            Explore Expand Excel
          Heading link



 
Copy link












                            Explore
                    

                Explore all your new UIC and Chicago homes have to offer
            












                            Expand
                    

                Expand as you apply your learning to real world challenges and gain transferable skills while leaving your mark.
            












                            Excel
                    

                Excel by showcasing what you have learned during your journey, proving you are Real World Ready!
            
















